<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.3">
<l>taṭavarai yiṉmītē caraṟkāla cantira</l>
<l>ṉiṭaiyuvā vilvan teḻuntālē pōlnīyum</l>
<l>vaṭamaturai yārmaṉṉaṉ vācutēvaṉ kaiyiṟ</l>
<l>kuṭiyēṟi vīṟṟiruntāy kōlap peruñcaṅke.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O big, beautiful conch! You too are sitting majestically,</l>
<l>settling in the hand of Vāsudeva, the King of the people of Northern Mathurā,</l>
<l>like the autumnal moon that came and rose above a vast mountain</l>
<l>during a full moon [night]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
